## Limitations

This report is based on data available up to October 2023, and the situation may have evolved since then. Additionally, the analysis relies on publicly available information, which may not capture all nuances of the global oil market. Future developments in geopolitical tensions, economic policies, and technological advancements in energy production could further influence gas prices.